front.abstract:
This specification describes the supplementary services belonging to the group line identification supplementary services. The group of line identification supplementary services is divided into the following four supplementary services:
CLIP:	calling line identification presentation (clause 1);
CLIR:	calling line identification restriction (clause 2);

COLP:	connected line identification presentation (clause 3);
COLR:	connected line identification restriction (clause 4).
